    <note>Index year algorithmically generated: Rule 3; 本貫潼川府銅山縣; Zhao(1) Zhengyuan [27629] This is an interesting case. His eldeer brother, Yinlong [27630], is identified in the 1256 jinshi list as earning the degree in the same year, wujia #186. Zhengyuan's grandfather is identified as the founder of the family, whereas Yinlong's father is so identified. Zhengyuan's mother is identified as a born Wang(2), whereas Yinlong's mother is identified as a born Han(1). Yinlong's entry has him as a Mingshan resident, whereas Sichuan TZ, 123.54a records address as Tongshan, same as Zhengyuan. Both father and great grandfather's names are missing in Yinlong's entry although Yu [27631] is recorded as the grandfather of both. CBD, 4, 3421-2.</note>
